find(a){
 if(parent[a] < 0){
    return a;
 }else{
 int x = find(parfent[a]);
 parent[a] = x;
 return x;
 }
}

union(a , b){
 parent[a] = min(parent[a] , parent[b]);
 parent[b] = a; 
}

solution

for the querry
2 4
find(2) = 1;
find(4) = 1;
return TIE;

for the 2nd query
2 3
find(2) = 1
find(3) = 5
parent[1] > parent[5]
winner 3;

as we are storing negative values
